{"type": "article", "id": 16749, "title": "小型洗衣机", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-29T07:20:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110620ZXURT7FO4yvra8oI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是韩国设计师 Kyumin Ha 设计的小型洗衣机，看上去近似一个榨汁机。上面的圆筒可以加入衣服，下面放水和洗衣液，然后就只需等待了。不过，体积太小也限制了它的功能，不能脱水排水，是一个半自动的洗衣机，因而它更加适合个人清理小型衣物，作为大型洗衣机的附属。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144040RShou18sxWTdNcFI.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"1031\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144040AnWjCqcR2Ifw9Qm1.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"311\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.29619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144041vaHZSlb0TtoEc5KD.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"743\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261440420Dk6TIyZ3jz5Qxer.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"1050\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}